about.summary: A collection of Machine Learning utilities

name: eo-learn-ml-tools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "eo-learn-ml-tools" %}
{% set version = "0.6.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 20387b52c58fadef303c8aad3ec7e69442729a822b0ecd8a043087eb80c2ca91

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - eo-learn-core
    - matplotlib-base
    - pandas
    - python >=3.5
    - scikit-image
    - seaborn

test:
  imports:
    - eolearn
    - eolearn.ml_tools

about:
  home: "https://github.com/sentinel-hub/eo-learn"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "A collection of Machine Learning utilities"
  doc_url: "https://pypi.org/project/eo-learn-ml-tools/"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/sentinel-hub/eo-learn"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mwilson8
    - dcunn
    - oblute
    - rluria14
    - benhuff
